item.title: About me
item.description: Hello! My name is Cade Cluche. I am a maker and hacker from Huntsville, Alabama. I attend the Alabama School of Cyber Technology and Engineering as a freshman. My personal interests include Linux, tinkering, 3D printing, hacking, and sometimes programming. Thank you for visiting my website! Have a wondeful day Cade Cluche
